                  <additions><list><item xml:id="a1">Prayers and name chart, fol. 2rv</item><item xml:id="a2">Note of ownership by Mammerē (f. 1a) and by Bēta Giyorgis (f. 24a)</item><item xml:id="e1">Pen trial by Gabra Māryām (f 1b). Stamp of the Institute of Ethiopian Studies, ff. 1a and 147b</item></list></additions>
